      name: 'KitchGuard 3L Wet Chemical',
      description: 'Specialized kitchen fire extinguisher designed to handle fires involving cooking oils and fats (Class F/K). Reacts chemically with the hot oil to create a cooling, soap-like layer that cuts off oxygen.',
